<p>&#8216;Extended family members seeking to provide long-term, stable care for vulnerable children will be able to access free legal advice, thanks to new government investment announced today (30 April 2023).&#8217;</p>
<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/news/family-members-taking-on-vulnerable-children-to-receive-better-legal-support">Full Story</a></p><p>Ministry of Justice, 1st May 2023</p><p>Source: <a href="https://www.gov.uk">www.gov.uk</a></p>